hardware-almanac.com

File hierarchy:
hardware-almanac 			- root folder
	index.html/index.css 	 - home page
	common.css			     - global stylesheet
	responsive.css			 - device compatibility style (UNUSED)
	resources			     - global resources folder
	page				     - child page (i.e. memory) folder
		page.html		
		page.css          - child stylesheet
		subpage			- child subpage (i.e types of memory) folder
			subpage.html
			subpage.css

CSS Documentation

All pages inherit from common.css. Individual page styling and page-unique features
should remain in that page's own .css file.

classes:
	.page_title - for the "hardware-almanac.com" title
	.page_title+h4 - for the "A Comprehensive Guide..." subtitle

	.centered - for any text that needs to be align: center
	article .heading - any article header, bigger version of .heading
	.nav_bar - the container for navigation buttons
	.nav_button - navigation buttons inside the nav_bar
	.center_content - elements under the header in the center. Elements inside of a center_content will be aligned side-by-side from the middle branching out. 
    .aligned_left - elements within center_content that need to be at the left edge

